Package: libflex0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: FLEX paging protocol encoder/decoder library
 libflex is a C library for encoding and decoding Motorola FLEX paging
 protocol messages. It provides a frame encoder, streaming decoder,
 BCH(31,21) error correction with 2-bit correction, block interleaving,
 multi-speed support (1600/3200/6400 bps), and numeric, alphanumeric,
 binary, and tone-only message types.

Package: libflex-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libdevel
Depends: libflex0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: FLEX paging protocol encoder/decoder library (development files)
 libflex is a C library for encoding and decoding Motorola FLEX paging
 protocol messages.
 .
 This package contains the header files and pkg-config file needed
 to build programs that use libflex.
